Pricing

Everything you need, nothing you don’t

No sign-up fee

No monthly fee

No obligation

Sign up for free

One simple fee

You will only be charged when you make money.

We deduct a fee (5% Travelnest fee + 15% channel commission) from the total value of each booking at the time payment is made to you.

This fee is applicable for bookings where a guest stays, or for cancelled bookings where the guest does not receive a full refund.

*plus VAT where applicable

5% Travelnest fee

£5

15% channel commission

£15

Paid to you

Paid to you

£80

Based on a 1 night stay at £100 per night

On average, getting just 4 extra bookings through Travelnest will cover all fees and commissions for the entire year.

Earn even more money with a Travelnest Direct hosted website and avoid paying any channel commission.
